Please.You guys qualify for
the friends and family plan.

45
00:02:09,850 --> 00:02:10,910
I don't know what that means.

46
00:02:11,260 --> 00:02:12,640
Speaking of families...

47
00:02:12,980 --> 00:02:15,590
Oh,yeah,that's unbelievable.Figure
your kid's dead...

48
00:02:15,820 --> 00:02:18,240
Then after 15 years,Patrick
shows up at the front door.

49
00:02:18,450 --> 00:02:21,130
How does a 14-year-old evade
an international manhunt?

50
00:02:21,250 --> 00:02:22,190
When was the last time you saw him?

51
00:02:22,330 --> 00:02:23,890
The summer before my junior year.

52
00:02:24,430 --> 00:02:26,900
Oh,I fell in love with Europe.

53
00:02:27,740 --> 00:02:31,880
We were going to museums in every city,and it
was one of the best tutoring jobs I ever had.

54
00:02:32,180 --> 00:02:35,200
