Switzerland,and I never heard from him again.

55
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:38,310
Must be nice to have a father who
welcomes you home with old masters.

56
00:02:38,530 --> 00:02:40,760
He wanted a lot of new pieces
before the homecoming party.

57
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:45,440
Oh,well,it will be nice to see him and
William,and,wow,Bea was just a baby.

58
00:02:45,770 --> 00:02:46,670
And of course Stanton.

59
00:02:46,830 --> 00:02:48,430
- Who's Stanton?
- The butler.

60
00:02:48,610 --> 00:02:50,230
He was kind of the glue that
kept the family together.

61
00:02:50,390 --> 00:02:53,620
Just one butler?Very
frugal for gazillionaires.

62
00:02:53,810 --> 00:02:57,080
Okay,I'm leaving.Hey,by the way,I'm
gonna be putting alarms on the art.

63
