Come on.The Mortensen Real Estate
scandal's not gonna solve itself.

66
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,970
I wish it would.

67
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,570
Mrs.Burke.Do come in.

68
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:27,470
Stanton,you still can call me Elizabeth.

69
00:03:27,660 --> 00:03:30,390
Unfortunately,I cannot.

70
00:03:32,070 --> 00:03:33,050
Good day.

71
