Thanks to Elizabeth's recommendation,William
hired me as your replacement.

196
00:10:20,070 --> 00:10:22,130
Excuse me.You?

197
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:24,050
Rhett Carlyle,domestic artist.

198
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:26,370
He buttled in a castle in Hampshire.

199
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:28,700
- It's a verb.
- I am aware.

200
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:32,580
How long did you work in Hampshire?

201
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,890
Till he was caught with a princess.

202
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,900
Suspected.Never caught.

203
00:10:36,470 --> 00:10:38,460
But the evidence was overwhelming.

204
00:10:39,460 --> 00:10:40,710
I didn't steal the silverware.

205
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:44,100
There is more to private service than
consorting with the landed gentry.

206
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:48,280
In addition to scheduling
valet and chauffeur duties,

207
00:10:48,470 --> 00:10:51,040
one needs to develop an
acute sense of observation.

208
00:10:51,170 --> 00:10:54,080
You wear your Oxfords with a
luster,not a shine,lattice-laced.

209
00:10:54,250 --> 00:10:57,750
Carpal tunnel in your wrist,probably
from years of pouring from the right.

210
00:10:58,230 --> 00:11:01,960
- And,Peter...Peter.
- Yes.

211
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:06,120
Muscle fatigue,dry
lips,watery eyes,nausea--

212
00:11:06,900 --> 00:11:10,610
I am a brilliant study,and this man has the
flu,so you might want to keep your distance.

213
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:17,340
My life's work has been protecting
that family.I want that to matter.

214
00:11:17,980 --> 00:11:22,170
Then tell me everything I need to
know about taking care of the Wolcotts.

215
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:31,140
Carlyle.

216
00:11:34,190 --> 00:11:35,560
Chauncey's ready for his walk.

217
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,590
Thank you,Miss Bea.

218
00:11:37,650 --> 00:11:40,530
There's a reading of Franny
and Zooey at the 92nd Street Y.

219
00:11:41,010 --> 00:11:42,570
