245
00:13:19,540 --> 00:13:20,520
Ibuprofen?

246
00:13:21,070 --> 00:13:22,350
The daytime stuff,the nighttime stuff?

247
00:13:22,990 --> 00:13:24,060
What about the pink stuff?

248
00:13:40,310 --> 00:13:41,260
Okay.

249
00:13:47,010 --> 00:13:48,930
- Peter Burke.
